Package edu.citadel.cvm.assembler

Enum Symbol

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Symbol>
      • edu.citadel.cvm.assembler.Symbol
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Symbol>, java.lang.constant.Constable
    public enum Symbol
extends java.lang.Enum<Symbol>
    This class encapsulates the symbols (also known as token types) for the CVM assembly language.
